n him.<br/><br/>When we killed him he gave zero faction adjustments, zero experience, and zero loot, not even cash. So Frankely (hehe sorry), I don't believe anybody camped this guy from level 55 to 58 because from what I've seen, he's darn near impossible to kill, and doesn't give any experience in that level range anyway.<br/><br/>That said, I'll continue to kill him whenever I get the people together, just because its kinda fun, and you never know, I could be wrong.<br/><br/>Nefarius Frobozz, Level 56 magician<br/>Terris Thule</p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
